A chess club named after the weakest piece on the board. “For new and experienced players, in that order.”

@pawnchessclub started with one spontaneous chat over drinks that turned into their first event. Now they’re running pop-ups for strangers who want to learn, friends who want to play, and a community that keeps getting bigger.

A Notion-powered side quest that turned into something more ♟️
